Installation and apply best practices for OCP4 AWS

creds - Config file for OCP4 Installation

./1_bastion-prepare.sh - Prepare pre-existed Bastion host in AWS
./2_create-cluster.sh - Install CLuster
./3_applyday2ops.sh - Apply Day2Ops, Apply best practices
./4_setup-ceph.sh - Install Ceph(Spin up additional nodes, install oeprator and cluster itself)
./5_setup-argocd.sh - Install ArgoCD
./6_setup-openstack.sh - Install Openshift on ArgoCD
./99_destroy-cluster.sh - Destroy OCP4 cluster
